rlm-git-changed

Pick a file changed since the fork point of the current branch from
the default remote branch (origin/HEAD) using fzf, then open it in
$EDITOR. The diff preview for the selected file is shown in the fzf
preview pane. Press Ctrl-P to cycle the preview pane height.

ENVIRONMENT
  EDITOR   Editor to open the selected file (falls back to vi).

REQUIRES
  git, fzf
